d The Prophet said, \u201cIf you do a bad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21900,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/12\/sent-prophet-perfect-good-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":17563,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Morals: Allah sent the Prophet to perfect good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has sent me with the perfection of noble morals and completion of good deeds.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 7073 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/good-character-heaviest-mizan\/","url_meta":{"origin":17563,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character is heaviest on the Scale","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing is heavier upon the scale of a believer on the Day of Resurrection than his g